[
  {
    "time_sec": 12.807,
    "speaker_role": "excited_fan",
    "text": "白热化阶段",
    "volume": 0.93,
    "priority": 0.7,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_front",
    "duration_sec": 1.44,
    "can_overlap_crowd": true,
    "tts_mix_type": "excited_commentary_over_cheer",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.7
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 50.07,
    "speaker_role": "angry_fan",
    "text": "有利进攻，吹什么",
    "volume": 0.86,
    "priority": 0.78,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_left",
    "duration_sec": 2.1,
    "can_overlap_crowd": true,
    "tts_mix_type": "dispute_over_tension",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.36
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 82.707,
    "speaker_role": "tactical_fan",
    "text": "法国没有一个能出球的",
    "volume": 0.81,
    "priority": 0.74,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_right",
    "duration_sec": 2.63,
    "can_overlap_crowd": true,
    "tts_mix_type": "analysis_over_ambient",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.4
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 100.973,
    "speaker_role": "neutral_fan",
    "text": "当时这个失误央视解说也说了，比较搞心态，我都以为法国大势已去了",
    "volume": 0.79,
    "priority": 0.82,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_back",
    "duration_sec": 7.51,
    "can_overlap_crowd": false,
    "tts_mix_type": "standalone_tts",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.22
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 116.337,
    "speaker_role": "tactical_fan",
    "text": "其实从这时候可以看出阿根廷开始有意拖时间了",
    "volume": 0.81,
    "priority": 0.82,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_front",
    "duration_sec": 5.25,
    "can_overlap_crowd": true,
    "tts_mix_type": "analysis_over_ambient",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.4
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 123.833,
    "speaker_role": "tactical_fan",
    "text": "2：0领先，76分钟，全队体能下降严重，是你你拖不拖时间",
    "volume": 0.81,
    "priority": 0.84,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_left",
    "duration_sec": 6.68,
    "can_overlap_crowd": true,
    "tts_mix_type": "analysis_over_ambient",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.4
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 184.31,
    "speaker_role": "excited_fan",
    "text": "开始了姆巴佩即将上演奇迹",
    "volume": 0.93,
    "priority": 0.84,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_right",
    "duration_sec": 3.11,
    "can_overlap_crowd": true,
    "tts_mix_type": "excited_commentary_over_cheer",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.7
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 208.118,
    "speaker_role": "tactical_fan",
    "text": "领先一方如果开始倒脚，南美球迷就会开始喊 Ole，每倒一脚喊一声 Ole。",
    "volume": 0.81,
    "priority": 0.87,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_back",
    "duration_sec": 8.51,
    "can_overlap_crowd": true,
    "tts_mix_type": "analysis_over_ambient",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.4
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 220.041,
    "speaker_role": "excited_fan",
    "text": "踢到这里本来以为要结束了，没想到小龟杀出来告诉你什么是卫冕冠军",
    "volume": 0.93,
    "priority": 0.91,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_front",
    "duration_sec": 7.57,
    "can_overlap_crowd": true,
    "tts_mix_type": "excited_commentary_over_cheer",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.7
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 232.425,
    "speaker_role": "tactical_fan",
    "text": "这里明显被生吃了，倒地把球解围出边线啊。",
    "volume": 0.81,
    "priority": 0.8,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_left",
    "duration_sec": 5.0,
    "can_overlap_crowd": true,
    "tts_mix_type": "analysis_over_ambient",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.4
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 242.757,
    "speaker_role": "excited_fan",
    "text": "点球！",
    "volume": 0.93,
    "priority": 0.97,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_right",
    "duration_sec": 1.1,
    "can_overlap_crowd": true,
    "tts_mix_type": "excited_commentary_over_cheer",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.7
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 245.393,
    "speaker_role": "tactical_fan",
    "text": "就是这个节点，当你以为赢了的时候，这时候就是致命的松懈。",
    "volume": 0.81,
    "priority": 0.95,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_back",
    "duration_sec": 6.84,
    "can_overlap_crowd": true,
    "tts_mix_type": "analysis_over_ambient",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.4
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 260.448,
    "speaker_role": "tactical_fan",
    "text": "上半场靠逼抢完全掌控局面，但是也消耗了太多体力",
    "volume": 0.81,
    "priority": 0.91,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_front",
    "duration_sec": 5.67,
    "can_overlap_crowd": true,
    "tts_mix_type": "analysis_over_ambient",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.4
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 268.275,
    "speaker_role": "tactical_fan",
    "text": "奥塔已经卡不住了，不犯规不行了",
    "volume": 0.81,
    "priority": 0.84,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_left",
    "duration_sec": 3.76,
    "can_overlap_crowd": true,
    "tts_mix_type": "analysis_over_ambient",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.4
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 279.164,
    "speaker_role": "angry_fan",
    "text": "最后一人不是红点吗？",
    "volume": 0.86,
    "priority": 0.81,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_right",
    "duration_sec": 2.67,
    "can_overlap_crowd": true,
    "tts_mix_type": "dispute_over_tension",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.36
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 282.296,
    "speaker_role": "neutral_fan",
    "text": "迪马利亚：有种不祥的预感。",
    "volume": 0.79,
    "priority": 0.75,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_back",
    "duration_sec": 3.33,
    "can_overlap_crowd": false,
    "tts_mix_type": "standalone_tts",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.22
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 288.475,
    "speaker_role": "neutral_fan",
    "text": "法国虽败犹荣，实力其实不输阿根廷",
    "volume": 0.79,
    "priority": 0.79,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_front",
    "duration_sec": 4.0,
    "can_overlap_crowd": false,
    "tts_mix_type": "standalone_tts",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.22
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 293.99,
    "speaker_role": "excited_fan",
    "text": "真正的比赛现在刚刚开始",
    "volume": 0.93,
    "priority": 0.85,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_left",
    "duration_sec": 2.87,
    "can_overlap_crowd": true,
    "tts_mix_type": "excited_commentary_over_cheer",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.7
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 299.22,
    "speaker_role": "excited_fan",
    "text": "准备天神下凡",
    "volume": 0.93,
    "priority": 0.84,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_right",
    "duration_sec": 1.68,
    "can_overlap_crowd": true,
    "tts_mix_type": "excited_commentary_over_cheer",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.7
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 309.251,
    "speaker_role": "excited_fan",
    "text": "最戏剧性的来了，两分钟扳平了。",
    "volume": 0.93,
    "priority": 0.97,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_back",
    "duration_sec": 3.81,
    "can_overlap_crowd": true,
    "tts_mix_type": "excited_commentary_over_cheer",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.7
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 314.23,
    "speaker_role": "excited_fan",
    "text": "完了，这一下炸了。",
    "volume": 0.93,
    "priority": 0.94,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_front",
    "duration_sec": 2.38,
    "can_overlap_crowd": true,
    "tts_mix_type": "excited_commentary_over_cheer",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.7
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 316.855,
    "speaker_role": "tactical_fan",
    "text": "姆巴佩的点球罚得好，有力度，有角度。",
    "volume": 0.81,
    "priority": 0.89,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_left",
    "duration_sec": 4.46,
    "can_overlap_crowd": true,
    "tts_mix_type": "analysis_over_ambient",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.4
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 326.382,
    "speaker_role": "excited_fan",
    "text": "两分钟梅开二度",
    "volume": 0.93,
    "priority": 0.94,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_right",
    "duration_sec": 1.92,
    "can_overlap_crowd": true,
    "tts_mix_type": "excited_commentary_over_cheer",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.7
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 331.922,
    "speaker_role": "tactical_fan",
    "text": "这球挺悬的，差一点扑救成功",
    "volume": 0.81,
    "priority": 0.83,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_back",
    "duration_sec": 3.29,
    "can_overlap_crowd": true,
    "tts_mix_type": "analysis_over_ambient",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.4
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 337.209,
    "speaker_role": "tactical_fan",
    "text": "这个角度很刁钻了",
    "volume": 0.81,
    "priority": 0.79,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_front",
    "duration_sec": 2.15,
    "can_overlap_crowd": true,
    "tts_mix_type": "analysis_over_ambient",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.4
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 343.017,
    "speaker_role": "tactical_fan",
    "text": "马丁判断方向真的强",
    "volume": 0.81,
    "priority": 0.83,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_left",
    "duration_sec": 2.39,
    "can_overlap_crowd": true,
    "tts_mix_type": "analysis_over_ambient",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.4
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 352.074,
    "speaker_role": "tactical_fan",
    "text": "大马丁判断都对了，就是姆巴佩太极限了",
    "volume": 0.81,
    "priority": 0.91,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_right",
    "duration_sec": 4.48,
    "can_overlap_crowd": true,
    "tts_mix_type": "analysis_over_ambient",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.4
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 370.772,
    "speaker_role": "excited_fan",
    "text": "这回轮到阿根廷人汗流浃背了",
    "volume": 0.93,
    "priority": 0.84,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_back",
    "duration_sec": 3.35,
    "can_overlap_crowd": true,
    "tts_mix_type": "excited_commentary_over_cheer",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.7
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 384.837,
    "speaker_role": "neutral_fan",
    "text": "当年看直播的时候真的是惊心动魄，现在知道结局再看就好很多。",
    "volume": 0.79,
    "priority": 0.77,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_front",
    "duration_sec": 7.14,
    "can_overlap_crowd": false,
    "tts_mix_type": "standalone_tts",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.22
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 396.491,
    "speaker_role": "tactical_fan",
    "text": "金斯利·科曼从梅西脚下断走了球。",
    "volume": 0.81,
    "priority": 0.93,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_left",
    "duration_sec": 3.86,
    "can_overlap_crowd": true,
    "tts_mix_type": "analysis_over_ambient",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.4
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 403.668,
    "speaker_role": "tactical_fan",
    "text": "中场已经失去控制了",
    "volume": 0.81,
    "priority": 0.91,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_right",
    "duration_sec": 2.39,
    "can_overlap_crowd": true,
    "tts_mix_type": "analysis_over_ambient",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.4
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 409.512,
    "speaker_role": "tactical_fan",
    "text": "其实看慢放，马丁内斯碰到了，但是这么快的低平球很难扑。",
    "volume": 0.81,
    "priority": 0.96,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_back",
    "duration_sec": 6.6,
    "can_overlap_crowd": true,
    "tts_mix_type": "analysis_over_ambient",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.4
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 421.908,
    "speaker_role": "neutral_fan",
    "text": "确实是永生难忘的世界杯决赛",
    "volume": 0.79,
    "priority": 0.84,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_front",
    "duration_sec": 3.35,
    "can_overlap_crowd": false,
    "tts_mix_type": "standalone_tts",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.22
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 425.876,
    "speaker_role": "tactical_fan",
    "text": "为什么推开十八号？必须留一名球员在对方半场，否则对方可以直接开球。",
    "volume": 0.81,
    "priority": 0.92,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_left",
    "duration_sec": 8.13,
    "can_overlap_crowd": true,
    "tts_mix_type": "analysis_over_ambient",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.4
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 436.37,
    "speaker_role": "neutral_fan",
    "text": "当时我看见梅西笑我就知道稳了",
    "volume": 0.79,
    "priority": 0.79,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_back",
    "duration_sec": 3.58,
    "can_overlap_crowd": false,
    "tts_mix_type": "standalone_tts",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.22
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 444.666,
    "speaker_role": "neutral_fan",
    "text": "难拿，才足以证明世界杯的含金量，才足以值得梅西花十几年去追。",
    "volume": 0.79,
    "priority": 0.92,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_front",
    "duration_sec": 7.32,
    "can_overlap_crowd": false,
    "tts_mix_type": "standalone_tts",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.22
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 452.881,
    "speaker_role": "excited_fan",
    "text": "八十二分钟落后一球，敢这么射门也是大心脏。",
    "volume": 0.93,
    "priority": 0.91,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_left",
    "duration_sec": 5.23,
    "can_overlap_crowd": true,
    "tts_mix_type": "excited_commentary_over_cheer",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.7
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 468.971,
    "speaker_role": "tactical_fan",
    "text": "细节：大马丁已经碰到球了，也埋下了点球大战的伏笔。",
    "volume": 0.81,
    "priority": 0.94,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_right",
    "duration_sec": 6.13,
    "can_overlap_crowd": true,
    "tts_mix_type": "analysis_over_ambient",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.4
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 477.388,
    "speaker_role": "excited_fan",
    "text": "这脚倒地抽射真的帅",
    "volume": 0.93,
    "priority": 0.87,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_back",
    "duration_sec": 2.39,
    "can_overlap_crowd": true,
    "tts_mix_type": "excited_commentary_over_cheer",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.7
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 483.931,
    "speaker_role": "tactical_fan",
    "text": "凌空贴地，这个球门将能碰到就是极限了，能不能改变轨迹完全看天意",
    "volume": 0.81,
    "priority": 0.97,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_front",
    "duration_sec": 7.51,
    "can_overlap_crowd": true,
    "tts_mix_type": "analysis_over_ambient",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.4
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 495.915,
    "speaker_role": "tactical_fan",
    "text": "但是，马丁内斯的扑救方向全是对的。",
    "volume": 0.81,
    "priority": 0.89,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_left",
    "duration_sec": 4.28,
    "can_overlap_crowd": true,
    "tts_mix_type": "analysis_over_ambient",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.4
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 509.624,
    "speaker_role": "neutral_fan",
    "text": "但是阿根廷真的很坚韧、很专注。换作其他球队，这时心态可能已经崩了，但他们还是一直咬牙挺到了最后。",
    "volume": 0.79,
    "priority": 0.96,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_right",
    "duration_sec": 9.5,
    "can_overlap_crowd": false,
    "tts_mix_type": "standalone_tts",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.22
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 531.02,
    "speaker_role": "neutral_fan",
    "text": "阿根廷这个冠军含金量十足。全队团结、坚强、拼命，胜不骄、败不馁，逆境中也没有放弃。",
    "volume": 0.79,
    "priority": 0.97,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_back",
    "duration_sec": 9.5,
    "can_overlap_crowd": false,
    "tts_mix_type": "standalone_tts",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.22
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 550.24,
    "speaker_role": "neutral_fan",
    "text": "德保罗说：当比分被扳平时，我们整个身体都开始崩溃，是梅西站出来鼓舞了我们。",
    "volume": 0.79,
    "priority": 0.91,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_front",
    "duration_sec": 8.93,
    "can_overlap_crowd": false,
    "tts_mix_type": "standalone_tts",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.22
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 573.234,
    "speaker_role": "tactical_fan",
    "text": "这次防守是只防突破吗？觉得姆巴佩一定会内切打门，结果他直接选择了传中。",
    "volume": 0.81,
    "priority": 0.88,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_left",
    "duration_sec": 8.61,
    "can_overlap_crowd": true,
    "tts_mix_type": "analysis_over_ambient",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.4
  },
  {
    "time_sec": 585.643,
    "speaker_role": "tactical_fan",
    "text": "门将跳早了。",
    "volume": 0.81,
    "priority": 0.7,
    "spatial_anchor": "seat_right",
    "duration_sec": 1.72,
    "can_overlap_crowd": true,
    "tts_mix_type": "analysis_over_ambient",
    "preferred_crowd_duck_volume": 0.4
  }
]